org.jgap
Interface IPersistentRepresentation

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractSupergene, BaseChromosome, BooleanGene, Chromosome, CompositeGene, DoubleGene, FixedBinaryGene, IntegerGene, MapGene, MyChromosome, NickelsPenniesSupergene, Population, SetGene, StringGene
public interface IPersistentRepresentation

Interface for objects that can represent themselves as a string and parse this string later on to generate a new instance of themselves.

Since:
3.2
